{"id":280425,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-500名上海民众到市信访办抗议，一名示威者/","date":"2013-02-22T14:45:54Z","modified":"2013-02-22T14:45:54Z","title":"维权网 | 500名上海民众到市信访办抗议，一名示威者被当场抓走（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>星期三上午，上海市政府信访办门前的人民大道上，聚集着约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>名遭遇司法不公、医疗事故、劳动争议、征收土地、房屋强拆、因反腐败被拘留劳教的上访维权人士。他们在这条血泪上访路上苦苦抗争多年，依然寻不到公正。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当天，在人群中特别引人注目的是一位手持“司法腐败不公百姓无处讲理”标语的年轻女访民。她拿着标语爬上树，将标语挂在树枝上，高呼口号：“打倒腐败、打倒贪官”。</span><span> </span><span>上访维权人士和游客共一千多人围观，在树底下一边称赞示威女访民的勇气，一边谴责司法腐败源于权大于法，独裁体制造成人权灾难。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>女访民在树上示威不到三分钟，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span><span>多名警察迅速赶来驱赶围观者，并拉出警戒线，用命令的口气喊叫示威者下来。女访民坚持维护《中国人民共和国宪法》第三十五条赋予的权利，继续高呼：“打倒腐败、打倒贪官”。一名警察由其他警察抬到树上抓示威女访民，一会儿示威女访民被警察从树上拉下来塞进警车开走，不知去向。女访民被警察抓走后，紧接着一位男访民欲爬上树示威，被警察阻止。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网将持续关注示威女访民的情况，了解详情后作进一步报道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kefcUWmiz1o/USb3q_WjGeI/AAAAAAAAdrY/HkigKldlRvE/s1600/P1000913.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kefcUWmiz1o/USb3q_WjGeI/AAAAAAAAdrY/HkigKldlRvE/s320/P1000913.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mCF9qKrNxEo/USb3rbKWKVI/AAAAAAAAdrg/GOd2biuUebw/s1600/P1000914.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-mCF9qKrNxEo/USb3rbKWKVI/AAAAAAAAdrg/GOd2biuUebw/s320/P1000914.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QiYCti0DjSw/USb3sL4rh2I/AAAAAAAAdro/QMIVMB0msX0/s1600/P1000916.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-QiYCti0DjSw/USb3sL4rh2I/AAAAAAAAdro/QMIVMB0msX0/s320/P1000916.JPG\" width=\"268\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w7H5q2EKD9A/USb3txF6KkI/AAAAAAAAdrw/DodeK3KE8vE/s1600/P1000919.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-w7H5q2EKD9A/USb3txF6KkI/AAAAAAAAdrw/DodeK3KE8vE/s1600/P1000919.JPG\" width=\"254\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-77a4zL6LDf0/USb3vzlvt7I/AAAAAAAAdr4/o74I3ITPCkk/s1600/%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E8%BE%B9%E7%A7%B0%E8%B5%9E%E4%B8%8A%E6%A0%91%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%A5%B3%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%BE%B9%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%85%90%E8%B4%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E6%B3%95P1000909.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-77a4zL6LDf0/USb3vzlvt7I/AAAAAAAAdr4/o74I3ITPCkk/s1600/%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E8%BE%B9%E7%A7%B0%E8%B5%9E%E4%B8%8A%E6%A0%91%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%A5%B3%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8B%87%E6%B0%94%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E8%BE%B9%E8%B0%B4%E8%B4%A3%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%85%90%E8%B4%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%BA%90%E4%BA%8E%E6%9D%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E6%B3%95P1000909.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nnYXMuQg1lI/USb3ykDOrmI/AAAAAAAAdsA/Is8tS5uiGjk/s1600/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%8A%E6%A0%91%E6%8A%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85P1000918.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-nnYXMuQg1lI/USb3ykDOrmI/AAAAAAAAdsA/Is8tS5uiGjk/s1600/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%8A%E6%A0%91%E6%8A%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85P1000918.JPG\" width=\"263\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-keaqgxdKFTU/USb31Tx6eEI/AAAAAAAAdsI/f76G5NFl4Hc/s1600/%E5%B